record.jsxtip: Fires after the user clicks this button or when this button has focus and the user presses the spacebar or Enter key. Also fired after the user presses the bound hot key (Key Binding property), if any. This event is also fired by the doExecute() method of the ToolbarButton class. Canceling this event prevents the Change event from firing.
